{"tid":559661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為吸收足夠營養，大笨象互相用鼻塞肛，直接挖屎嚟食","createTime":"2018-02-13T11:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T12:12:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac051861bb41f1cae5777ffbee1cbfa32932dd2","tid":559661,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"英國《每日郵報》近日分享一段影片，有一隻大象在眾目睽睽之下，當場把整個象鼻塞進另一隻同伴大象的肛門裡，隨後更從同伴的肛門裡挖糞食用，慢慢品嘗。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_4268f507f5a40400dadbbe32bd3586bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_4268f507f5a40400dadbbe32bd3586bb.jpg&h=67417622&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180213/1297670/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297670%2F&d=jsqmDAceei3L%2FEVJ%2FIjPbr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=48b0c2a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297670%2F&h=d09cf529\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180213/1297670/</a>"},{"pid":"997278db694b6e55a98ea5d3a4970c4a5529702f","tid":559661,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"影片可見，現場目擊的民眾們紛紛驚聲尖叫，不敢相信這隻大象竟會把象鼻塞肛、掏糞吃大便，《每日郵報》不禁形容：「我到底是看到了什麼？ (What did I just watch?)」網友們也紛紛說：「我在吃早餐讓我看到這個，完全沒食慾了。」、「趕快救出這隻大象啊，牠一定是餓壞了。」、「我知道有的大象會吃自己的糞便，但我第一次看到塞肛挖糞的。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_784e0e3255b254b3f1972db30dffb4b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_784e0e3255b254b3f1972db30dffb4b8.jpg&h=f9565986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">食得津津有味<img src=\